     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                    ExampleNTST History file
                    ------------------------
This file should be used by the G4 example coordinator to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
     ----------------------------------------------------------

December 5th, 2012  John Allison
- Migrated to DrawTrajectory (i_mode argument no longer available).

June 13th, 2012  Gabriele Cosmo
- Explicit inclusion of units and constants headers.
- Fixed shadowing compilation warnings...

February 2nd, 2012  John Apostolakis
- Improved Exceptions in NTSTPhysicsList.cc

October 26th, 2011  John Apostolakis
- Moved to separate Multiple Scattering processes 
   * necessary for recent G4 versions. 
   Changed NTSTPhysicsList (with Vladimir Ivantchenko's help)

November 9th, 2005  Gabriele Cosmo
- Migrated to <sstream> and std:: namespace.

May 27th, 2003  John Apostolakis
- Ported to gcc 3.2.
- Deleted all Bgs classes.

July 1998 David Williams
- Started from ExampleN02.
